metadata.name: NB4
metadata.description:
NB4 is a stunning piece that showcases the power of AI technology in the world of art. Through my signature style, I explore the concept of the Mandela effect and bring it to life through my artwork.

The artwork features Logos/objects and fashion that are often associated with the modern era, in a setting that dates back to 1666. The juxtaposition of these two elements creates a thought-provoking image that challenges the viewer to reconsider their understanding of time and history.
